OL,3,CScotland 'paid price' of 20 years of
OL,4,CSNP says Scottish Labour on eve of poll
OL,6,FThe Scottish Labour leader said
OL,7,FScotland has "paid the price" from 20
OL,8,Fyears of the SNP and urged voters to
OL,9,Freject Reform.
OL,11,FSpeaking a day before the polls open
OL,12,Ffor the Holyrood elections, Scottish
OL,13,FLabour leader Anas Sarwar is expected
OL,14,Fto say the choice is between the SNP's
OL,15,Fre-election or a new Scottish Labour
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,18,FHe will focus on the "struggling" NHS
OL,19,Fand is expected to say many people
OL,20,F"feel they are paying more and getting
OL,21,Fless".
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@]O]zD@VOUzD@aO]|D@AOU}D@EO]
