OL,3,CScotland 'paid price' of 20 years of
OL,4,CSNP says Scottish Labour on eve of poll
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead to the party's eve of
OL,7,Fpoll rally, Mr Sarwar said: "We have
OL,8,Fall seen the mess John Swinney and the
OL,9,FSNP have made over those 20 years.
OL,11,F"Our NHS is struggling, family budgets
OL,12,Fare under pressure and too many people
OL,13,Ffeel they are paying more and getting
OL,14,Fless.
OL,16,F"The SNP has had 20 years and Scotland
OL,17,Fhas paid the price ` give me five, and
OL,18,Ftogether we can build a better future."
OL,26,@oD@]OUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@gO]
