OL,3,CScotland 'paid price' of 20 years of
OL,4,CSNP says Scottish Labour on eve of poll
OL,6,FMr Sarwar added that voters have seen
OL,7,Fthe damage of 20 years of SNP
OL,8,Fgovernment in an NHS under pressure,
OL,9,Ffamily budgets stretched to breaking
OL,10,Fpoint, young people denied
OL,11,Fopportunities and communities left
OL,12,Fbehind.
OL,14,FHe also urged voters to reject the
OL,15,F"poison of Reform" as the party said
OL,16,FReform UK has been offering smears and
OL,17,Fgrievance instead of answers.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@RO]
