OL,3,CScotland 'paid price' of 20 years of
OL,4,CSNP says Scottish Labour on eve of poll
OL,6,FMr Sarwar continued: "Only Scottish
OL,7,FLabour can win in constituencies
OL,8,Facross Scotland, beat the SNP and
OL,9,Fdeliver the change Scotland needs.
OL,10,FTomorrow, Scotland faces a simple
OL,11,Fchoice:
OL,13,F"More of the same with John Swinney
OL,14,Fand the SNP, or change with Scottish
OL,15,FLabour. The poison of Reform, or a
OL,16,Fbetter future for our country.
OL,26,@nD@VOUuD@AOU
