OL,3,CScotland 'paid price' of 20 years of
OL,4,CSNP says Scottish Labour on eve of poll
OL,6,F"I'm standing to fix the mess, get the
OL,7,Fbasics right and build a better future
OL,8,Ffor Scotland. So my message to voters
OL,9,Fis simple. Tomorrow, vote for change.
OL,10,FReject Reform. Beat the SNP. Change
OL,11,FScotland. Vote Scottish Labour."
OL,13,FSNP campaign director Angus Robertson
OL,14,Fsaid: "Anas Sarwar has nothing
OL,15,Fpositive to offer Scottish voters `
OL,16,Fall he wants to do is stop the SNP
OL,17,Fgetting things done.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@`O]vD@GOU
