OL,3,CScotland 'paid price' of 20 years of
OL,4,CSNP says Scottish Labour on eve of poll
OL,6,F"A re-elected SNP government will
OL,7,Fsupport people with the soaring cost
OL,8,Fof living by introducing a price cap
OL,9,Ffor essential food items in
OL,10,Fsupermarkets, cut energy bills and
OL,11,Fopen more GP walk-in clinics all over
OL,12,FScotland to help beat the 8am rush `
OL,13,FLabour and the other parties just want
OL,14,Fto stop us.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
