OL,3,CScotland 'paid price' of 20 years of
OL,4,CSNP says Scottish Labour on eve of poll
OL,6,F"By backing John Swinney's reliable
OL,7,Fand trusted leadership on Thursday,
OL,8,Fpeople can elect an SNP majority for a
OL,9,Fgovernment which will support people
OL,10,Fwith the cost of living, lock Nigel
OL,11,FFarage out of power in Scotland, and
OL,12,Fdeliver the fresh start of
OL,13,Findependence."
OL,15,FReform UK has been approached for
OL,16,Fcomment.
